# Agent-generated scratch at repo root — these filenames are characteristic
# of what native-executor agents produce mid-session. Keeping them out of
# `git add -A` prevents the 14k-file accident from 2026-04-17.
/bug_report_*.md
/*_summary.md
/*-summary.md
/*-findings.md
/*-synthesis.md
/audit-*.md
/comprehensive-*.md
/consolidated-*.md
